##More than 300 million students suspended from school after 30,000 confirmed cases outside China

Micro Signal China Business Journal

Function introduction, grow in step with Chinese enterprises, talk with business leaders, spread business ideals, serve business people, "China Business News" control of the absolute voice of Chinese business.

According to the People's Daily, the latest data released by the World Health Organization showed that as of 10:00 central European time (17:00 China Standard Time) , the number of confirmed cases of new pneumonia outside China increased by 4105 from the previous day to 32,778; The number of deaths outside China increased by 186 to 872 from the previous day.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
According to UNESCO, the spread of NCP has led to the suspension of classes in many countries, affecting nearly 363 million students from pre-primary to higher education around the world.

#Italy has confirmed more than 10,000 deaths, 631

According to the latest data released by the Italian Ministry of Health at 18:00 local time on March 10, there are 8,514 cases of new coronavirus in Italy, 631 deaths, and 1,004 cured cases, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 10,149, there were 977 new cases and 168 new deaths since 18:00 on March 9.

Italian Prime Minister Contes said in a televised speech on the evening of the 9th, in order to avoid the spread of the new pneumonia epidemic, from the 10th to implement a citywide lockdown. People throughout the country are not allowed to leave their places of residence without permission, except for three special reasons: demonstrable work, health and urgent needs.

While strengthening the epidemic prevention measures, Italy is also actively looking for foreign aid. According to the Foreign Ministry website on the evening of the 10th News, State Councilor and Foreign Minister Wang Yi was asked to make a phone call with Italian Foreign Minister Dima. Dima said that the current situation in Italy is very serious, the Italian government is closely watching and learning from China's successful experience in fighting the epidemic, to take strong measures to stop the spread of the epidemic. The Italian side is faced with the difficulty of shortage of medical materials and equipment, and hope that China will help solve the urgent problem.

Wang Yi said that although China still has a large demand for medical supplies, we will overcome the difficulties, provide medical supplies such as masks to Italy, and increase our efforts to export urgently needed supplies and equipment to Italy. If the Italian side needs, the Chinese side is also willing to send a medical team to help fight the epidemic.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Department of Health diagnosed with new coronary pneumonia

Department of Health Chief Nutting Doris has been diagnosed with new coronary pneumonia, according to the People's Daily. She is understood to have met hundreds of people in Parliament in the past week and attended a reception with British Prime Minister Johnson at the 10 Downing Street. Doris developed symptoms on Friday and was diagnosed on the evening of the 10th local time, the report said.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Greece has announced the closure of all schools in the country

Greek Prime Minister Mitsotakis announced on the afternoon of March 10 local time that the government had decided to close all schools and universities in Greece for 14 days to control the spread of the new coronavirus, China Daily reported. Mitsotakis stressed that the Greek government will use the 14 days to reduce the spread of new pneumonia, strengthen the Greek medical capacity. As of the afternoon of 10 March, 89 cases had been confirmed in Greece, with no deaths.

The number of confirmed cases of new coronary pneumonia in Spain increased to 1,695

As of 22:00 local time on October 10,1695 cases of new pneumonia in Spain, 35 deaths. Madrid, the capital, was the worst affected, with 782 cases.

In an effort to contain the rapidly developing outbreak, the Spanish government announced a number of measures on March 10, including the suspension of all direct flights between Spain and Italy from March 11 to 25 and the closing of sporting events in Spain. In addition, a member of the West House of Representatives also confirmed 10 new coronavirus infection, the house announced that the next week will be adjourned.

Source: China Youth Daily (reporter, Han Shuo) , CCTV news (reporter, Wei Fan) , overseas website, China Daily, official website of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs, etc. .
